addition to "Transfer Orders" and "Payment Orders"? If yes, why, and
what are they good for? If no, what is the system that decided when
the rules use shorthand and when they spell out "Transfer" or
"Payment" Orders? If it is merely to save space, shorthand could have
been used more often. If there are other reasons, they have escaped me
so far (not that it would surprize me very much :)

