It's not nearly as hard as all that. You convince the Assessor e's somehow
made a mistake in totalling, reporting, &c. your number of VTs. If e's
convinced, e'll admit a COE about it and you get the money. Only if anyone
else raises an issue do you need to convince anyone else. 


